{"title":"插秧","authors":["刘章"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"插秧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河北兴隆半壁山公社　刘章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白花花的水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青葱葱的山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花海滚滚接蓝天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛在云里吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器绕山转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻秧层层浪花翻……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记插秧在田间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦不尽头上的汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡亲们的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妙过活神仙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金银线，钢铁针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缝的山区好春天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们笑哈哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙把山歌编："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“钢铁针，金银线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山区永住好春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千线万线一根头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党交给咱们总路线！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}